import {
  Container,
  FormControl,
  FormControlLabel,
  FormHelperText,
  InputLabel,
  TextField,
} from "@material-ui/core"

const Login = () => {
  return (
    <Container maxWidth="xs">
      <form>
        <FormControl>
          <TextField
            variant="outlined"
            margin="normal"
            required
            fullWidth
            id="email"
            label="Email Address"
            name="email"
            autoComplete="email"
            autoFocus
          ></TextField>
        </FormControl>
      </form>
      <FormControl>
        <InputLabel htmlFor="email">Email Address</InputLabel>
        <input id="email" aria-describedby="email-helper-text"></input>
        <FormHelperText id="email-helper-text">
          Please enter your email.
        </FormHelperText>
      </FormControl>
    </Container>
  )
}

export default Login
